trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref>, <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart"></xref>, and <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref>, <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart"> </xref>, og <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: CatalogPartDesigner is a multi-purpose designer that provides design-time rendering for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> controls, which both inherit from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> base class.
trans-unit.target: CatalogPartDesigner er en flere formålet designer som gir utformingen gjengivelse og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>kontrollerer som begge arver fra <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>basere klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: CatalogPartDesigner serves as a standard control designer, adding only what customization is needed to validate the associated control and apply its design mode state to the design-time rendering.
trans-unit.target: CatalogPartDesigner fungerer som standard kontrollen designer legger til bare hvilken tilpassing kreves for å validere den tilknyttede kontrollen og gjelder tilstanden for spørringsutforming modus for utforming gjengivelse.

trans-unit.source: If you have a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> control, you can create a derived designer, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner>, to provide design-time rendering.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du har en egendefinert <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>kontrollen, kan du opprette en avledet utformer eksempel <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner>, angi utformingen gjengivelse.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: You can safely override any of the members as needed; however, when overriding the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A> method, be sure to call the base implementation to avoid losing design mode state information.
trans-unit.target: Du kan overstyre alle medlemmene trygt etter behov. imidlertid når overstyrer den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A>metoden, Husk å kalle base implementeringen for å unngå å miste tilstandsinformasjon for utforming-modus.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Creates a copy of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> control to render at design time.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en kopi av det tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> kontrollen skal gjengi ved utformingen.

trans-unit.source: This method is overridden to copy zone information to the view control.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden overstyres for å kopiere informasjon om til visningskontrollen.

trans-unit.source: A copy of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: En kopi av det tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Verifies that the control resides in a zone of type <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"></xref>, and then gets the markup that is used to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Bekrefter at kontrollen befinner seg i en sone av typen <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"> </xref>, og henter markup som brukes til å representere kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The markup that is used to represent the control at design time, or error markup if the control does not reside in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Koden som brukes til å representere kontrollen under utformingen eller feil markup Hvis kontrollen ikke finnes i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Binds the designer to the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref>-derived control.
trans-unit.target: Binding designer til det tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref>-avledet kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref>-derived control associated with the designer.
